### Markdown Reference

  [text](url)
  [text][tag]
  [tag]: url
  ## to ##### (there's # and 6x# but are rarely used)
  _ italics, * bold (around text)
  ![name](image)  displays the image
  > block quote
  • list 
  number. will make a numbered list
  force a newline with double spaces at end of line (tighter paragraphs)
